title: I opened hextach key and get nothing
body:
I got 3 key frags.
I made a key.
I clicked "Open" on my stack of chests.
The chest and key were consumed, but I didn't gain anything.
I thought it was a bug, so I reset my client a couple of times, but nothing changed.

replies.body: When did this occur?  I don't see any transactions since the 7th, but there's been some maintenance so it may not be updating for me just yet.  If this is still an issue, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so the support team can see what happened.  We'll get back to you as soon as we can!
